section#submit-proposal
  .submit-proposal-container
    h2 Contact us
    p.p-footer
      | If you have an idea or project you'd like to collaborate on or if you found a bug, we'd love to hear from you. Submit a private message through this form. In case you have a public proposal that you wish to be voted, you can do so by logging into your account. If it's a great fit for our community, we'll work together to bring it to life and reward you with tokens and NFTs.

    form(id="form-footer", action="#" method="post")
      label(for="name") Name
      input#name(type="text" name="name" required)
      label(for="email") Email
      input#email(type="email" name="email" required)
      label(for="proposal") Proposal
      textarea#proposal(name="proposal" rows="10" cols="50" placeholder="Write your proposal here.." required)
      button.apply-button(type="submit") Submit Proposal

